---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base title="about">
  <section class="about">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <hr class="rule" />
    <p>
      I'm Drew. I work on software and think about mathematics. This site
      collects notes, observations, and the occasional longer essay on
      topics that hold my attention: algorithms, type theory, systems
      design, and whatever else I happen to be reading.
    </p>
    <p>
      The site is statically generated from MDX with KaTeX for typesetting
      and published to GitHub Pages. You can subscribe via <a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .about h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about p {
    text-align: left;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
</style>
